---\ntitle: 紫微斗数指南\ndescription: The complete guide to Zi Wei Dou Shu — Chinese Destiny Astrology (紫微斗数)\ntemplate: splash\nhero:\n  title: 紫微斗数\n  tagline: 紫微斗数 · Zi Wei Dou Shu\n  image:\n    html: |\n      <div class=\"hero-orbit\">\n        <div class=\"orbit-ring orbit-ring-1\"></div>\n        <div class=\"orbit-ring orbit-ring-2\"></div>\n        <div class=\"orbit-ring orbit-ring-3\"></div>\n        <div class=\"orbit-center\">\n          <span class=\"orbit-star\">紫</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"orbit-dot dot-1\"></div>\n        <div class=\"orbit-dot dot-2\"></div>\n        <div class=\"orbit-dot dot-3\"></div>\n        <div class=\"orbit-dot dot-4\"></div>\n      </div>\n  actions:\n    - text: 开始学习 · Start Learning\n      link: /guides/what-is-zi-wei/\n      icon: right-arrow\n      variant: primary\n    - text: 探索星曜 · Explore Stars\n      link: /stars/overview/\n      icon: external\n---\n\nimport { Card, CardGrid } from '@astrojs/starlight/components';\n\n<div class=\"home-calligraphy\">观星悟道 · 知命立命</div>\n\n<div class=\"home-intro\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>紫微斗数</strong>（Zi Wei Dou Shu），又称「帝王学」，是中国古代最精密的命运预测体系之一。\n    起源于宋代，历经千年传承，以<strong>108颗星曜</strong>与<strong>十二宫位</strong>构建完整人生图谱。\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    与西方占星不同，紫微斗数不仅揭示性格特质，更深探命运轨迹、运势起伏与人生关键时刻。\n    本指南以现代英文，系统教授这一古老智慧。\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"traditional-divider\">◈ 探索之旅 ◈</div>\n\n<CardGrid stagger>\n  <Card title=\"什么是紫微斗数？\" icon=\"seti:book\">\n    了解这门千年智慧的起源、核心理论与东西方占星差异。从入门到精通的第一步。\n    [<strong>入门指南</strong> →](/guides/what-is-zi-wei/)\n  </Card>\n  <Card title=\"十四颗主星\" icon=\"seti:star\">\n    紫微、天机、太阳……十四主星各掌天命。本站详述每颗星的性情、事业、财富、感情全解。\n    [<strong>星曜总览</strong> →](/stars/overview/)\n  </Card>\n  <Card title=\"十二宫位\" icon=\"seti:layout\">\n    命宫、财帛宫、事业宫、夫妻宫……十二宫位呈现人生全景。了解各宫含义与星曜配置。\n    [<strong>宫位总览</strong> →](/palaces/overview/)\n  </Card>\n  <Card title=\"命盘解读实例\" icon=\"seti:search\">\n    从名人命盘到年度运势，学习如何将理论应用于实践。\n    [<strong>案例分析</strong> →](/cases/celebrity-charts/)\n  </Card>\n</CardGrid>\n\n<div class=\"traditional-divider\">◈ 星曜速查 ◈</div>\n\n<div class=\"star-grid\">\n\n<a class=\"star-card\" href=\"/stars/zi-wei/\">\n  <span class=\"star-chinese\">紫微</span>\n  <span class=\"star-english\">Zi Wei · Emperor Star</span>\n  <span class=\"star-desc\">帝王之星，统御诸星，主宰命运</span>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"star-card\" href=\"/stars/tian-ji/\">\n  <span class=\"star-chinese\">天机</span>\n  <span class=\"star-english\">Tian Ji · Strategy Star</span>\n  <span class=\"star-desc\">谋略智慧，机变灵动，策划之心</span>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"star-card\" href=\"/stars/tai-yang/\">\n  <span class=\"star-chinese\">太阳</span>\n  <span class=\"star-english\">Tai Yang · Sun Star</span>\n  <span class=\"star-desc\">光明炽热，权力声望，男性力量</span>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"star-card\" href=\"/stars/wu-qu/\">\n  <span class=\"star-chinese\">武曲</span>\n  <span class=\"star-english\">Wu Qu · Military Star</span>\n  <span class=\"star-desc\">刚毅果断，财富之星，金属之气</span>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"star-card\" href=\"/stars/lian-zhen/\">\n  <span class=\"star-chinese\">廉贞</span>\n  <span class=\"star-english\">Lian Zhen · Chastity Star</span>\n  <span class=\"star-desc\">情欲之星，爱恨交织，复杂而深刻</span>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"star-card\" href=\"/stars/tian-tong/\">\n  <span class=\"star-chinese\">天同</span>\n  <span class=\"star-english\">Tian Tong · Harmony Star</span>\n  <span class=\"star-desc\">福泽之星，温和快乐，享乐与满足</span>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"star-card\" href=\"/stars/tian-yong/\">\n  <span class=\"star-chinese\">天梁</span>\n  <span class=\"star-english\">Tian Yong · Supervisor Star</span>\n  <span class=\"star-desc\">监察之星，保护智慧，长者之德</span>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"star-card\" href=\"/stars/ji-men/\">\n  <span class=\"star-chinese\">巨门</span>\n  <span class=\"star-english\">Ji Men · Hidden Star</span>\n  <span class=\"star-desc\">隐藏之门，复杂沟通，深层洞察</span>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"star-card\" href=\"/stars/lu-cun/\">\n  <span class=\"star-chinese\">禄存</span>\n  <span class=\"star-english\">Lu Cun · Fortune Star</span>\n  <span class=\"star-desc\">财富积累，稳健积累，物质繁荣</span>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"star-card\" href=\"/stars/tian-kong/\">\n  <span class=\"star-chinese\">天空</span>\n  <span class=\"star-english\">Tian Kong · Void Star</span>\n  <span class=\"star-desc\">虚空之象，哲学精神，超然物外</span>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"star-card\" href=\"/stars/tao-hua/\">\n  <span class=\"star-chinese\">桃花</span>\n  <span class=\"star-english\">Tao Hua · Romance Star</span>\n  <span class=\"star-desc\">桃红之运，浪漫魅力，艺术美感</span>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"star-card\" href=\"/stars/zuo-fu-you-bi/\">\n  <span class=\"star-chinese\">左辅 · 右弼</span>\n  <span class=\"star-english\">Zuo Fu & You Bi · Assistants</span>\n  <span class=\"star-desc\">辅弼双星，辅助之力，伙伴与支持</span>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"star-card\" href=\"/stars/qing-yang/\">\n  <span class=\"star-chinese\">青羊 · 博士</span>\n  <span class=\"star-english\">Qing Yang & Bo Xu · Scholars</span>\n  <span class=\"star-desc\">学术权威，专业造诣，知识的力量</span>\n</a>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"home-footer-poem\">\n  <p>\n    星移斗转，命随数定。<br/>\n    知命而立命，观星以悟道。\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"poem-author\">—— 紫微斗数</p>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n/* Homepage-only decorative styles */\n.home-calligraphy {\n  font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;\n  font-size: 2.8rem;\n  text-align: center;\n  color: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.35);\n  letter-spacing: 0.5em;\n  margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem;\n  line-height: 1.2;\n}\n\n.home-intro {\n  max-width: 680px;\n  margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n.home-intro p {\n  font-size: 1.08rem;\n  color: #b8a888;\n  line-height: 1.9;\n  margin-bottom: 0.8em;\n}\n\n.home-intro strong {\n  color: #e8c96e;\n}\n\n.home-footer-poem {\n  text-align: center;\n  margin-top: 2.5rem;\n  padding: 1.5rem;\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.05), transparent);\n  border-top: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.15);\n  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.15);\n}\n\n.home-footer-poem p {\n  font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;\n  font-size: 1.15rem;\n  color: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.5);\n  margin: 0;\n  line-height: 1.8;\n}\n\n.home-footer-poem .poem-author {\n  font-size: 0.9rem !important;\n  margin-top: 0.5rem !important;\n  opacity: 0.7;\n}\n\n/* Hero SVG animation */\n.hero-orbit {\n  position: relative;\n  width: 160px;\n  height: 160px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n\n.orbit-ring {\n  position: absolute;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.2);\n  animation: orbit-spin linear infinite;\n}\n\n.orbit-ring-1 { width: 60px; height: 60px; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); animation-duration: 8s; }\n.orbit-ring-2 { width: 100px; height: 100px; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); animation-duration: 14s; animation-direction: reverse; border-style: dashed; }\n.orbit-ring-3 { width: 140px; height: 140px; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); animation-duration: 20s; border-color: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.1); }\n\n.orbit-center {\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 50%; left: 50%;\n  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n  width: 50px; height: 50px;\n  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.3), transparent);\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\n  font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;\n  font-size: 1.4rem;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #c9a84c;\n  text-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.6);\n}\n\n.orbit-dot {\n  position: absolute;\n  width: 6px; height: 6px;\n  background: #c9a84c;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.8);\n  animation: orbit-spin linear infinite;\n}\n\n.dot-1 { top: 50%; left: calc(50% + 26px); transform: translate(-50%, -50%); animation-duration: 8s; }\n.dot-2 { top: calc(50% - 46px); left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, 50%); animation-duration: 14s; }\n.dot-3 { top: 50%; left: calc(50% - 66px); transform: translate(-50%, -50%); animation-duration: 14s; animation-direction: reverse; }\n.dot-4 { top: calc(50% + 66px); left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); animation-duration: 20s; animation-direction: reverse; width: 4px; height: 4px; }\n\n@keyframes orbit-spin {\n  from { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg); }\n  to { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(360deg); }\n}\n</style>\n